TITLE: Creating a BottomSheetKeyboardAwareScrollView Component for @gorhom/bottom-sheet
DESCRIPTION: This code creates a custom BottomSheetKeyboardAwareScrollView component that combines KeyboardAwareScrollView with @gorhom/bottom-sheet functionality. It uses Reanimated and HOCs from bottom-sheet to create a compatible scrollable component.

