DESCRIPTION: A custom implementation of a keyboard animation hook that changes softInputMode only when the screen is focused. This hook uses React Navigation's useFocusEffect to ensure proper softInputMode management in navigation stacks, setting to adjustResize when focused and restoring the default mode when unfocused.

