DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use KeyboardAwareScrollView from react-native-keyboard-controller to handle keyboard interactions properly. It creates a custom TextInput component that extends React Native's TextInput with additional styling and then renders multiple instances of this component within a keyboard-aware scrollable container. The component automatically adjusts its position when the keyboard appears.

